Package: nif
Title: Build and Explore NONMEM Input Format Data Sets from Clinical Study Data
Version: 0.57.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Rainer", "Strotmann", email = "rainer.strotmann@mailbox.org",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0543-7984"))
Description: A System to Convert Study Data Tabulation Model (SDTM) Formatted
    Data into Longitudinal Data Tables Suitable for Nonlinear Mixed Effects
    Modeling (NONMEM). Aggregate Drug Administrations, PK/PD Observations and
    Covariates in a Stepwise Manner. Explore, Summarize and Visualize SDTM and
    NONMEM Data Sets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/rstrotmann/nif,
    https://rstrotmann.github.io/nif/reference/index.html
